{"word":"Captive","slug":"captive","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Captive</b> Prisoner of war<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=12'>Gen 14:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=30&verse=2'>1Sa 30:2</a><br/> Cruelty to:<br/> - Putting to death<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=20'>Num 31:20</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=20&verse=13'>Deu 20:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=21&verse=10'>Deu 21:10</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=8&verse=29'>Jos 8:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=10&verse=40'>Jos 10:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=11&verse=11'>Jos 11:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=7&verse=25'>Jdg 7:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=8&verse=21'>Jdg 8:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=21&verse=11'>Jdg 21:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=15&verse=33'>1Sa 15:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=2'>2Sa 8:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=8&verse=12'>2Ki 8:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=39&verse=6'>Jer 39:6</a> <br/> - Twenty thousand, by Amaziah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=25&verse=12'>2Ch 25:12</a> <br/> - Ripping women with child<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=8&verse=12'>2Ki 8:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=15&verse=16'>2Ki 15:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=30&chapter=1&verse=13'>Amo 1:13</a> <br/> - Tortured under saws and harrows<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=12&verse=31'>2Sa 12:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=20&verse=3'>1Ch 20:3</a> <br/> - Blinded<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=16&verse=21'>Jdg 16:21</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=39&verse=7'>Jer 39:7</a> <br/> - Maimed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=1&verse=7'>Jdg 1:7</a> <br/> - Ravished<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=25&chapter=5&verse=13'>Lam 5:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=14&verse=2'>Zec 14:2</a> <br/> - Enslaved<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=20&verse=14'>Deu 20:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=5&verse=2'>2Ki 5:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=44&verse=12'>Psa 44:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=3&verse=6'>Joe 3:6</a> <br/> - Robbed<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=23&verse=26'>Eze 23:26</a> <br/> - Confined in pits<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=51&verse=14'>Isa 51:14</a> <br/> - Other indignities to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=20&verse=4'>Isa 20:4</a> <br/> Kindness to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=30'>2Ki 25:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=106&verse=46'>Psa 106:46</a><br/> Advanced to positions in state<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=41&verse=45'>Gen 41:45</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=2&verse=8'>Est 2:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=27&chapter=1'>Dan 1</a>"}]}